 "html": "<p>By ons was Vrydae altyd visdae.  Ek het stokvis (hake) vir die gereg gebruik maar jy kan enige ferm witvis gebruik.  En ja, ek het n soppoeier gebruik. ( die kossnobs gril mos vir soppoeier). Die geheim van die gereg is om die vis nie te gaar te maak nie.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-037.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1508\" alt=\"vis blog 037\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-037-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>3 vismote ( ek het bevrore vis gebruik en voor die tyd dit laat ontdooi)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1499\" alt=\"vis blog 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>250 ml room<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1504\" alt=\"vis blog 015\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-015-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>1/2 pakkie wituiesop poeier<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1501\" alt=\"vis blog 007\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-007-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 houertjie sampioene<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1503\" alt=\"vis blog 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>visspesery as jy het<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1510\" alt=\"vis blog 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-003-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>sout en peper</li>\n<li>250 ml sterk kaas</li>\n<li>1 wieletjie feta</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>sny die vis in porsies en sit in jou oondbak<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-005.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1500\" alt=\"vis blog 005\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-005-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>gooi jou sout en peper en visspesery oor</li>\n<li>strooi die soppoeier oor<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1502\" alt=\"vis blog 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-008-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>sny die sampioene en gooi oor die vis</li>\n<li>gooi jou houer room oor<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-017.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1505\" alt=\"vis blog 017\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-017-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>maak die vis toe met foelie en bak in die oond vir 15 minute by 180 grade celsius</li>\n<li>na 15 minute haal die foelie af en strooi jou kaas oor die vis<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-025.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1506\" alt=\"vis blog 025\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-025-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bak nou oop vir nog 15 minute<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1507\" alt=\"vis blog 031\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-031-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Geniet die gereg met chips, groente of rys.  Maak n lekker bottel koue witwyn oop en gaan so die naweek rustig binne.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-045.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1509\" alt=\"vis blog 045\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/vis-blog-045-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
